task.summary: Added GUI elements to support the upcoming feature of device selection for Semble and ANZ
Updated Help Activity design and content
Disabled Help Activity as I believe it provides no helpful information. Moved some Help Contact info into the Contact Activity
Removed unused imports and fixed a bug which added the same Semble devices to Vodafone list even though they were meant to be in 2Degrees and Spark
Removed code that attemps to find Help Preference that no longer exists
Added better support for upcoming feature that allows users to pick their spoofing device
Improving Spoofing by allow user to select Spoof Device
Newline for human readable device name for Samsung S7 Edge
Added code to dynamically display the Spoof Device used shown to the user
Added ProGuard for release compile which helps reduce the resultant APK as well
Added Commenting for class and methods naming for newer versions of TVNZ and 3NOW
Promoted threading (AsyncTask) to avoid running code execution on UiThread
Disable debug preference if debug mode is enabled by hard-coding
Rewrote string for the Main Activity's Preference Fragment's Debug preference's summary value.
Added some commenting and logging method hooks for Semble
Testing git push after Git Config changes
Support for ANZ GoMoney v.5.4.2 and TVNZ OnDemand v2.5.1 added.
Added Supported for ANZ GoMoney NZ v5.5.2 (No backwards compatibility).
Merged global variables into Common Class.
Removed static keyword from DEBUG as it's no longer needed.
Added Transitions overrides when entering/leaving activities.
Attempt at fixing Travis CI #8 (Build continues on Lint failure).
